data.description: Great house with a Pool! Wonderful opportunity here for VA loan assumption if you qualify. Centrally located and offering lots of room to spread out and entertain and with loads of extras ! Nice sized bedrooms with great closet space . Spacious eat in kitchen with island and a  window overlooking the inground pool, covered patio and fenced backyard. Den with vaulted ceilings and fireplace. Extra room off hallway is referred to as the Dining Room but could  also make a great office/playroom. Garage is heated and cooled and previously used as an exercise room. Located in a prize winning school district, this house is sure to please. House has never flooded and is located in flood zone x, a preferred flood zone with lower cost flood insurance.12x16 work shed ! Refrigerator, washer and dryer and audio visual equipment all stay ! Easy access to shopping, Doctors ,Hospitals and major highways.Call your agent for details regarding the VA assumption . 2023-11-13
